long_description: Use the ripstop polyester Big Agnes Tensleep Station 6 footprint under your Big Agnes Tensleep Station 6 tent to protect its floor from abrasion and wear. Sizing specific to the tent prevents water from pooling between the tent and footprint in rainy weather. Webbing stake-outs at tent corners provide easy attachment.
